        "metaTitle": "Petty Cash Dual Control Requirements | Petty Cash",
        "title": "Petty Cash Dual Control Requirements",
        "metaDescription": "Discover how effective dual control helps businesses reduce waste, improve financial control, and build a culture of cost consciousness that drives long-term profitability.",
